                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6876" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">BL-0031</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11234 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">康美造假独董连带赔偿上亿，不“独”不“懂”时代结束</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Kangmei’s bearing huge compensation exposes the independent directors’ lack of independence or professionalism</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">杨宏玲，杨叶</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西北工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">康美药业股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">医药卫生工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">虚假陈述； 独立董事； 连带责任； 公司治理</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">misrepresentation, independent director, joint liability, corporate governance</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作为一个值得载入A股发展史册的案件，康美药业集体诉讼案是证券法确立中国特色证券代表人诉讼制度后，首个适用该制度的案件。同时，判决中24.59亿的损失赔偿金额，也创下了国内上市公司证券市场虚假陈述民事诉讼案件的最高赔偿额纪录。康美药业因证券市场虚假陈述，不仅公司要承担责任，包括独立董事在内的公司高管多人，也都被判决承担上亿元的连带赔偿责任，引发上市公司独立董事辞职潮。本案例旨在从康美药业信息披露发生虚假陈述的原因出发，让学生学习独立董事勤勉义务的认定及其独立性和专业性在公司治理中的重要意义，体会独立董事在公司虚假陈述中承担责任的方式对独立董事制度的影响，进一步思考我国独立董事制度应如何完善，才能平衡其权利和风险，使其在公司治理中更好的发挥作用。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">As a case worthy of being recorded in the history of A-share development, the Kangmei Pharmaceutical Co.,Ltd. class action case is the first case to apply the securities representative litigation system with Chinese characteristics after the Securities Law established the system. At the same time, the 2.459 billion loss compensation amount in the judgment also sets a record for the highest compensation in a civil lawsuit for misrepresentation in the securities market of a domestic listed company. Due to the misrepresentation made by Kangmei to the securities market, not only Kangmei has to bear responsibility, but many senior executives of the company, including independent directors, have also been sentenced to bear joint and several liability for hundreds of millions of yuan, which triggered a wave of resignations of independent directors of listed companies. Starting from the reasons for misrepresentation in the information disclosure of Kangmei, this case aims to let students learn the identification of independent directors’ diligence obligations and the importance of independent directors’ independence and professionalism in corporate governance, and let students understand the impact on the independent director system of the way independent directors take responsibility for misrepresentation in the company, and further thinking about How we should improve the independent director system to balance its rights and risks and make it play a better role in corporate governance.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《商法》、《公司治理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">信息披露；虚假陈述责任；勤勉义务；独立董事的虚假陈述责任；独立董事制度与公司治理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-12</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
